   <main class="wp-block-group entry-content is-layout-constrained wp-container-core-group-is-layout-22 wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained" id="wp--skip-link--target"> 
    <div class="wp-block-group alignfull is-home-intro-banner is-layout-constrained wp-container-core-group-is-layout-5 wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained" style="padding-top:0rem;padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--edge-space);padding-bottom:0rem;padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--edge-space)"> 
     <div class="wp-block-columns alignwide is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-1 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex"> 
      <div class="wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow" style="padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--40);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--40);flex-basis:50%"> 
       <h1 class="wp-block-heading" style="font-size:70px">Meet WordPress</h1> 
       <p class="is-style-short-text">The open source publishing platform of choice for millions of websites worldwide—from creators and small businesses to enterprises.</p> 
      </div> 
      <div class="wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center has-link-color wp-elements-9ab46473c7797a5ad58ad1eba28f02b6 is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow" style="flex-basis:50%"> 
       <div class="wp-block-group is-layout-constrained wp-container-core-group-is-layout-4 wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained has-background" style="padding-top:2rem;padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--20);padding-bottom:2rem;padding-left:84px;background-image:url('https://wordpress.org/files/2024/06/wceu-bg-2.png');background-position:0% 0%;background-size:cover;"> 
        <div class="wp-block-group is-nowrap is-layout-flex wp-container-core-group-is-layout-2 wp-block-group-is-layout-flex" style="line-height:0"> <iframe width="320" height="180" src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/ELW4Jdvujbc?si=sE2V6C7oFHugIquT" title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe> 
        </div> 
        <div class="wp-block-group is-vertical is-layout-flex wp-container-core-group-is-layout-3 wp-block-group-is-layout-flex"> 
         <p class="is-style-short-text">Watch Cofounder Matt Mullenweg’s anticipated mid-year project update, recorded live from WordCamp Europe 2024.</p> 
         <p class="is-style-short-text"><a href="https://wordpress.org/news/2024/06/highlights-from-wordcamp-europe-2024/">Read the event recap</a></p> 
        </div> 
       </div> 
      </div> 
     </div> 
    </div> 
    <div class="wp-block-wporg-language-suggest alignfull has-background" style="background-color:#ebebeb"></div> 
    <div class="wp-block-group alignfull has-light-grey-2-background-color has-background is-layout-constrained wp-container-core-group-is-layout-6 wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained" style="padding-top:5rem;padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--edge-space);padding-bottom:5rem;padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--edge-space)"> 
     <div class="wp-block-columns alignwide is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-2 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex"> 
      <div class="wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow"> 
       <figure class="wp-block-image size-full has-custom-border">
        <img width="720" height="460" src="https://wordpress.org/files/2024/04/feature-style.png" alt="Illustration of various blocks, Paragraph and Cover." class="has-border-color has-light-grey-1-border-color wp-image-39764" style="border-width:1px;border-radius:4px" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/wordpress.org/files/2024/04/feature-style.png?w=720&amp;ssl=1 720w, https://i0.wp.com/wordpress.org/files/2024/04/feature-style.png?resize=300%2C192&amp;ssl=1 300w" sizes="(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px">
       </figure> 
       <h2 class="wp-block-heading has-inter-font-family" style="font-size:18px;line-height:1.88"><strong>Design</strong></h2> 
       <p class="is-style-short-text">Create any website with flexible design tools and the power of <a href="https://wordpress.org/blocks/" data-type="page" data-id="20359">blocks</a>. Start with a blank canvas or choose a <a href="https://wordpress.org/themes/" data-type="link" data-id="https://wordpress.org/themes/">theme</a>. Customize every detail—no code needed.</p> 
      </div> 
      <div class="wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow"> 
       <figure class="wp-block-image size-full has-custom-border">
        <img width="720" height="460" src="https://wordpress.org/files/2024/04/feature-build.png" alt="Illustration of an Image block with a block toolbar." class="has-border-color has-light-grey-1-border-color wp-image-39766" style="border-width:1px;border-radius:4px" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/wordpress.org/files/2024/04/feature-build.png?w=720&amp;ssl=1 720w, https://i0.wp.com/wordpress.org/files/2024/04/feature-build.png?resize=300%2C192&amp;ssl=1 300w" sizes="(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px">
       </figure> 
       <h2 class="wp-block-heading has-inter-font-family" style="font-size:18px;line-height:1.88"><strong>Build</strong></h2> 
       <p class="is-style-short-text">See how your site will look in real time, even as you add, edit, and rearrange content—with intuitive editing and integrated features to manage it all.</p> 
       <p><a href="https://wordpress.org/gutenberg/">Try the Block Editor</a></p> 
      </div> 
      <div class="wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow"> 
       <figure class="wp-block-image size-full has-custom-border">
        <img width="720" height="460" src="https://wordpress.org/files/2024/04/feature-publish.png" alt="Screenshot of the Twenty Twenty-Four theme." class="has-border-color has-light-grey-1-border-color wp-image-39765" style="border-width:1px;border-radius:4px" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/wordpress.org/files/2024/04/feature-publish.png?w=720&amp;ssl=1 720w, https://i0.wp.com/wordpress.org/files/2024/04/feature-publish.png?resize=300%2C192&amp;ssl=1 300w" sizes="(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px">
       </figure> 
       <h2 class="wp-block-heading has-inter-font-family" style="font-size:18px;line-height:1.88"><strong>Extend</strong></h2> 
       <p class="is-style-short-text">Make your site do whatever you need it to. Add a store, analytics, newsletter, social media integration; you’re in control with an extensive library of <a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/" data-type="link" data-id="https://wordpress.org/plugins/">plugins</a>.</p> 
      </div> 
     </div> 
     <div class="wp-block-columns alignwide is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-3 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex"> 
      <div class="wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow" style="flex-basis:50%"> 
       <div style="height:var(--wp--preset--spacing--20)" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div> 
       <h2 class="wp-block-heading has-heading-3-font-size">See what's new</h2> 
       <p class="is-style-short-text">Elevate your site-building experience with WordPress 6.5. This release includes a new way to manage fonts, exciting new foundational APIs for developers, and an impressive performance boost.</p> 
       <div class="wp-block-buttons is-layout-flex wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex"> 
        <div class="wp-block-button">
         <a class="wp-block-button__link wp-element-button" href="https://wordpress.org/download/releases/6-5/">Discover WordPress 6.5</a>
        </div> 
       </div> 
      </div> 
      <div class="wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow" style="flex-basis:50%"> 
       <figure class="wp-block-image size-full has-custom-border">
        <img width="1080" height="760" src="https://wordpress.org/files/2024/04/feature-whatsnew.png" alt="Mural illustration features new to WordPress 6.5, including: the aspect ratio feature, the Interactivity API, and the new Fonts Library." class="has-border-color has-light-grey-1-border-color wp-image-39769" style="border-width:1px;border-radius:4px" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/wordpress.org/files/2024/04/feature-whatsnew.png?w=1080&amp;ssl=1 1080w, https://i0.wp.com/wordpress.org/files/2024/04/feature-whatsnew.png?resize=300%2C211&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/wordpress.org/files/2024/04/feature-whatsnew.png?resize=1024%2C721&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/wordpress.org/files/2024/04/feature-whatsnew.png?resize=768%2C540&amp;ssl=1 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px">
       </figure> 
      </div> 
     </div> 
    </div> 
    <div class="wp-block-group alignfull has-white-color has-charcoal-1-background-color has-text-color has-background has-link-color wp-elements-27bb73a3f0c64a6b2ea9f494924da927 is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained" id="showcase" style="padding-top:5rem"> 
     <div class="wp-block-group alignfull is-layout-constrained wp-container-core-group-is-layout-9 wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained" style="padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--edge-space);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--edge-space)"> 
      <div class="wp-block-group alignwide is-layout-flow wp-container-core-group-is-layout-7 wp-block-group-is-layout-flow"> 
       <h2 class="wp-block-heading has-heading-2-font-size">One platform, a universe of possibilities</h2> 
       <div class="wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-4 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex"> 
        <div class="wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow" style="flex-basis:60%"> 
         <p class="is-style-short-text">Discover a collection of website examples from around the world, curated to spotlight gorgeous design, technical innovation, and the limitless power of WordPress.</p> 
        </div> 
        <div class="wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow" style="flex-basis:40%"></div> 
       </div> 
      </div> 
      <div class="wp-block-group alignwide wporg-home-showcase-logos is-content-justification-space-between is-layout-flex wp-container-core-group-is-layout-8 wp-block-group-is-layout-flex" style="margin-top:50px;margin-bottom:50px"> 
